features: Package includes: 9 pastel assorted colors folders, Includes colorful label stickers And it is easy to label, easy to read and easy to change.
High quality materials: Our folders are made of high quality plastic, unlike previous paper manila folders, the plastic ones are more durable, waterproof easy to clean and tear resistant.
Easy to use: The folders are in standard letter size of 8.6 x 11.6 inches, easily organize your files. With a crease at the bottom, the folder is expandable and can hold over 150 sheets of paper.
